sequenceDiagram
  participant User
  participant CreateBudget
  participant SelectExpenseTypeModal
  participant BudgetService
  participant Router

  User->>CreateBudget: Open Create Budget Screen
  CreateBudget->>User: Display Category and Amount Input
  User->>CreateBudget: Select Category
  CreateBudget->>SelectExpenseTypeModal: Open Modal to Select Category
  SelectExpenseTypeModal-->>CreateBudget: Return Selected Category

  User->>CreateBudget: Enter Amount
  User->>CreateBudget: Press Save Button
  CreateBudget->>BudgetService: Create Budget with selectedCategory and amount
  BudgetService-->>CreateBudget: Return Confirmation

  CreateBudget->>Router: Navigate to Budget Screen
  Router-->>User: Display Updated Budget List